# UCAB - Roles and Responsibilities

## Overview

The UCAB Cab Booking System follows a Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) model. The system consists of three main roles:

1. User (Rider)
2. Driver
3. Admin

Each role has specific responsibilities and permissions to ensure smooth and secure operation of the application.

---

## User (Rider)

The User is responsible for booking rides and managing personal travel activities.

### Responsibilities

- Register a new account
- Login securely into the application
- Search available cabs
- Book rides
- Track rides in real-time
- View booking history
- View payment receipts
- Manage profile information

### Features

- User Authentication
- Cab Booking
- Ride Tracking
- Ride History
- Payment Management

---

## Driver

The Driver is responsible for providing transportation services and managing ride requests.

### Responsibilities

- Login to the system
- View assigned ride requests
- Accept or reject ride requests
- Start and complete rides
- Update ride status
- View earnings
- Access ride history

### Features

- Driver Authentication
- Ride Management
- Status Updates
- Earnings Dashboard
- Ride History

---

## Admin

The Admin manages the overall platform and monitors system activities.

### Responsibilities

- Manage users
- Manage drivers
- Monitor ride bookings
- Track payment transactions
- Generate reports and analytics
- Add vehicle categories
- Remove vehicle categories

### Features

- User Management
- Driver Management
- Booking Monitoring
- Payment Monitoring
- Reports and Analytics
- Vehicle Category Management

---

## Role Relationship Diagram

```text
                   +-------------+
                   |    ADMIN    |
                   +-------------+
                          |
        -----------------------------------
        |                                 |
        v                                 v

+----------------+            +----------------+
|      USER      |            |     DRIVER     |
+----------------+            +----------------+
| Register/Login |            | Login          |
| Book Cab       |            | Accept Ride    |
| Track Ride     |            | Reject Ride    |
| Ride History   |            | Update Status  |
| Receipts       |            | View Earnings  |
+----------------+            +----------------+
```

---

## Role Permissions

| Function | User | Driver | Admin |
|-----------|------|--------|--------|
| Register/Login | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Book Cab | Yes | No | No |
| Track Ride | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Accept Ride | No | Yes | No |
| Update Ride Status | No | Yes | No |
| View Earnings | No | Yes | Yes |
| Manage Users | No | No | Yes |
| Manage Drivers | No | No | Yes |
| View Reports | No | No | Yes |
| Manage Vehicle Categories | No | No | Yes |

---

## Technologies Used

- React.js
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT Authentication
- Bootstrap

---

## Outcome

The Roles and Responsibilities module ensures secure access control, efficient ride management, and smooth administration of the UCAB Cab Booking System.

